{"name": "odoo14-addon-product-status", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-product-status", "version": "14.0.1.0.3", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-product-state", "odoo"], "summary": "Product Status Computed From Fields", "upload_time": 1710164573}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fproduct--attribute-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/product-attribute\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/14.0/product_status\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/product-attribute-14-0/product-attribute-14-0-product_status\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/product-attribute&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Product Status\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:5d66175e512c84518484889b820b568be2c612e708ee8198e0d18a3c909b1069\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module compute a status on product based on some date field\ndisplayed on the Sales tab.\nThis module will deactivate all default state in product_state,\nimplement new default data\nThe option to use the product-attribute/product_state module was\nconsidered but because the status is computed based on today. It does\nnot work well with a stored fields and also means there is no need for\ncreation of state from the user.\n\nBy order of importance, the status is computed by:\n\\- *End-of-life*\n\\- *Discontinued until*\n\\- *New until*\n\n*End-of-life* has priority over the other dates.\n*Discontinued-until* has priority over *New until*.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\nFile data/product_state_data.xml will be moved to demo/product_state_demo.xml since version 15.0\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues/new?body=module:%20product_status%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Camptocamp](https://www.camptocamp.com):\n  : - Thierry Ducrest \\<<mailto:thierry.ducrest@camptocamp.com>>\n    - Simone Orsi \\<<mailto:simahawk@gmail.com>>\n- [Trobz](https://trobz.com):\n  : - Son Ho \\<<mailto:sonhd@trobz.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\n**Financial support**\n\n- Cosanum\n- Camptocamp R&D\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/product-attribute](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/14.0/product_status) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_status.models..product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_state", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_status.models..product_state", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_status.models..product_template", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template.other_date_fields", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template.ProductTemplate", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template.ProductTemplate._onchange_end_of_life_date", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_status.models.product_template.ProductTemplate._onchange_discontinued_until", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "retu